Hi,

We have released a GPL Java Code Coverage tool, called: jcoverage.
Available from, http://jcoverage.com. jcoverage can report line and
branch coverage in HTML or XML. Sample reports (including those from
running the JUnit test cases) are available from:
http://jcoverage.com/jcoverage/samples/

The GPL binary and source code are available from:
http://jcoverage.com/download/jcoverage.html


We hope that you find it useful.
Regards,
Peter.
